metadata.name: FPX-Metaverse Club Card
metadata.description: The official FPX Metaverse Token Card NFT has become a means of hype by the project party, and has not been distributed to real fans. Our mission is to build a real Web3 community club for true FPX fans and explore a unique virtual world of FPX. Holders will enjoy multiple benefits such as membership, premium status and special airdrops. The first 1000 NFTs will be airdropped to those true fans gradually, while the remaining 1019 will open for public mint in the future.
